@@TJvCustomMonthCalendar
Summary
  Base component that serves as a wrapper around the MicroSoft® MonthCalendar control.
Description
  TJvCustomMonthCalendar is the base component for MicroSoft® MonthCalendar control wrappers. Never use
  a TJvCustomMonthCalendar control directly but rather one of its descendants. Currently JEDI-VCL
  provides you with one descendant: TJvMonthCalendar2.

