@@TJvCustomMonthCalendar.SetDayStates
Summary
  Sets the bold state for the currently visible days.
Description
  SetDayStates sets the bold state for the currently visible days.

  The method assumes the given array is at least the same size as the number of months currently
  visible (including partially visible months).

  It also assumes the first month in the array is the first (partially) visible month of the control.
Parameters
  MonthCount - Number of months to pass to the control
  DayStates  - Array with day states for each month. Must be large enough to hold MonthCount elements
                or the number of partially visible months, whichever is the largest. The first element
                is assumed to be the first (partially) visible month.

